settings.title: GOLDEN HOUR
settings.text: Our new Golden Hour collection is inspired by the mesmerising allure of the sunrise and sunset, enriching the soul with bold silhouettes and tantalising energy.

settings.title: SIGNATURE COLLECTION
settings.text: Embrace elegant simplicity with our curated edit of refined swimwear designed to celebrate the feminine form.

settings.title: WORSHIP THE SUN
settings.text: Our new Solari collection showcases timeless design and a rich sunset palette to inspire your holiday wardrobe.

settings.title: LUXE SWIM
settings.text: Featuring a luxurious French fabrication, our Ravello swimwear silhouettes are crafted with luxe gold thread and designed with tonal lines to flatter and elongate.

settings.title: ALLURE
settings.text: Neutral for the modern mindset, our Allure collection features best-selling silhouettes re-imagined in a contemporary new animal print.

settings.title: D'Orsay
settings.text: Abstract and monochromatic, our new D’Orsay collection features must-have staple styles for your next escape.

settings.title: Jetset Black
settings.text: Discover luxurious style for the modern woman with new resort and swim silhouettes from our best-selling JETSET collection.

settings.title: Versa Orchid
settings.text: Set the tone with our new Versa collection showcasing the perfect pop of orchid pink and contemporary design.

settings.title: Versa Blue
settings.text: Our Versa Collection features a suite of statement silhouettes enhanced through spliced fabrics from our signature palette.

settings.title: Lalita
settings.text: Turn heads in our new LALITA collection featuring a striking retro tonal print.

settings.title: Viva
settings.text: Discover hand painted tropical florals and exotic emerald hues with this season’s uplifting Viva collection.

settings.title: Desert Palm
settings.text: Discover sophisticated tonal dressing with our new Desert Palm collection.

settings.title: Animale
settings.text: Discover the ever classic animal print re-imagined with our Animale collection, available in an edit of staple silhouettes.

settings.title: JETS SUMMER 3 2022 SANCTUARY IN STYLE
settings.text: Escape to destinations afar with our Sanctuary In Style collection. Featuring Australian model and JETS muse Victoria Lee, the campaign is brought to life through a contemporary lens epitomising modern femininity and luxurious resort living.

settings.title: Ascenso
settings.text: Discover refined 70’s glamour with our new Ascenso collection featuring sophisticated swim and resortwear silhouettes.

settings.title: Raya
settings.text: Classic stripes are re-imagined with our new Raya collection, available in all your favourite JETS silhouettes.

settings.title: Palmas
settings.text: Discover modern femininity with our new Palmas swim and resortwear collection crafted with luxurious supportive swim fabrications available in an A-D cup.

settings.title: Rio
settings.text: Discover understated elegance with our new Rio collection featuring a unique textured wave fabrication available in all your favourite JETS silhouettes.

settings.title: Bonita
settings.text: Exude effortless femininity with our new Bonita collection featuring luxurious swim and resortwear designed to support A-DD cup.

settings.title: JETSET
settings.text: Discover Summer elegance with our new JETSET swim and resortwear. Crafted from luxurious body-sculpting fabric, discover our best-selling swimwear collection that will see you through the sun-soaked Australian Summer.

settings.title: Pantera
settings.text: Immerse yourself in our luxurious Pantera collection, with a new take on our best-selling animal print. Explore modern swim silhouettes and elegant resortwear staples designed to seamlessly mix in with your jet-setting wardrobe.

settings.title: Ipanema & JETSET
settings.text: Escape to lush exotic destinations with our Ipanema and JETSET collections. Refined silhouettes are uplifted in a luxurious chocolate colourway creating foundational styles for warm months ahead.

settings.title: Ipanema
settings.text: Discover subtle sophistication injected with vibrant palm greens with our Ipanema Collection. Seasonal styles will transport you to paradise and beyond.

settings.title: Paradiso
settings.text: Our new Paradiso collection will inspire your mind to wander, dream of exotic destinations afar, and escape to…PARADISE.

settings.title: Sahara
settings.text: Refresh your wardrobe with our new bold new seasonal print: SAHARA. The Sahara collection re-imagines seasonal staples with a bold new animal print available in swim and resortwear styles.

settings.title: Majorelle
settings.text: Revitalise your Spring wardrobe with our new Majorelle Collection. Paying homage to the artful botanics of Jardin Majorelle in Marrakech, this whimsical floral is brought to life through fabrics boasting a luminous feminine finish.

settings.title: JETS
settings.text: Let us take you on a journey to exotic Eastern destinations of your dreams. Custom prints draw inspiration from the silk route and historic textile designs. Liven your warm weather wardrobe with vibrant hues and contemporary JETS silhouettes designed in Australia.

settings.title: JETSET Resort
settings.text: Our best-selling core collection continues this season with a focus on timeless and minimalist design. Curate your warm weather wardrobe with our new range of JETSET resortwear designed to take you from daytime by the pool to an evening at the bar.

settings.title: JETSET Russet
settings.text: Let the latest hues of our JETSET swimwear range evoke vibrancy within your wardrobe. Our new Russet colourway was inspired by the earthy tones of Morocco and crafted with high quality body-sculpting fabric.
